[5] Cholera - India (Gujarat State)
Date: Wed 30 May 2012
Source: Daily News and Analysis (DNA) [edited]
http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report_5-cholera-cases-in-1-week-reported-in-gujarat_1695872


In the last 7 days 5 fresh cases of cholera were reported from Behrampura area of Ahmedabad, taking the total number of patients of the infectious disease to 9. 4 of the 5 cholera patients are admitted in AMC's [Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation] hospital for contagious diseases in Behrampura and one in LG Hospital. Against a total 8 cholera cases that were reported in Ahmedabad in 2011, 9 cases have already come to light in the city in 2012.

